---
title: Caramelised Pineapple & Pear Pavlovas with Mint Cream & Toasted Coconut 4 steps | Dessert | Serves 4+
description: Finish your dinner off with a sweet surprise! Load up these fruity delights with caramelised pear, pineapple and mint cream.
Sprinkle with toasted coconut for added crunch and it's a light and fresh dessert that is sure to please.
